CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FHarshita's father and sister spoke
OL,8,Fwith senior officers at
OL,9,FNorthamptonshire Police to demand
OL,10,Fanswers, as 18 months on, the man
OL,11,Fsuspected of killing her is still
OL,12,Fnowhere to be found.
OL,14,FThe 24-year-old was strangled in
OL,15,FNovember 2024. Her body was found in
OL,16,Fthe boot of a car four days later, by
OL,17,Fwhich time her husband, Pankaj Lamba,
OL,18,Fhad fled to India.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
