CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FFrustrated with the lack of progress,
OL,8,Fher family travelled to the UK from
OL,9,FIndia for the first time to put
OL,10,Fpressure on authorities to do more to
OL,11,Fcatch their daughter's killer.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News after meeting the
OL,14,Fsenior investigating officer in
OL,15,FHarshita's case, her sister, Sonia
OL,16,FDabas, said: "Words are the same,
OL,17,Fnothing is different. They did not
OL,18,Fgive us any new updates."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FBut she added the family will be
OL,8,Fleaving England with more hope that
OL,9,FPankaj Lamba will be caught.
OL,11,FHarshita and Lamba had an arranged
OL,12,Fmarriage in India in August 2023 and
OL,13,Fmoved to the UK in the spring of the
OL,14,Ffollowing year.
OL,16,FITV News understands that Lamba was in
OL,17,Fthe UK on a student visa and Harshita
OL,18,Fstarted working in a distribution
OL,19,Fcentre in Corby.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FBut shortly after moving here,
OL,8,FHarshita contacted Northamptonshire
OL,9,FPolice to say her new husband was
OL,10,Fabusing her.
OL,12,FShe was referred to a refuge and moved
OL,13,Fto another house in the area, while
OL,14,FLamba was arrested and bailed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
