PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FOn September 5 2024, a Domestic
OL,8,FViolence Protection Notice (DVPN) and
OL,9,Fa Domestic Violence Protection Order
OL,10,Fwere authorised at Northampton
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court, which remained in
OL,12,Fplace for 28 days while the
OL,13,Finvestigation continued.
OL,15,FBut after it lapsed, Lamba was free to
OL,16,Fcontact Harshita again and on November
OL,17,F10, it is believed she was murdered.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
