OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FHer body was found in the boot of
OL,8,FLamba's car in Ilford, east London,
OL,9,F100 miles away from his home in Corby,
OL,10,Ffour days later.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV News as we travelled
OL,13,Fwith her to the meeting with police,
OL,14,FSonia revealed she had told Harshita
OL,15,Fto come home after she reported the
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,F"I said to her to come back to India,
OL,19,Fmy father said just pack one bag,
OL,20,Fthere is no need to stay," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,F"It's the biggest misunderstanding.
OL,8,FShe was stuck here and she thought she
OL,9,Fwas safe."
OL,11,FShe said the family are being failed
OL,12,Fnow, just like Harshita.
OL,14,F"Everyone can see if we are being
OL,15,Ffailed now, you can imagine how
OL,16,FHarshita was treated. My focus is on
OL,17,FPankaj Lamba being arrested, then
OL,18,Fextradition. Where is he? Please tell
OL,19,Fme."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
