PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FHarshita's father, Satbir Singh,
OL,8,Fspeaks little English, but said: "UK
OL,9,Fpolice totally failed this case.
OL,10,FBritish police failed this case."
OL,12,FPoonam Joshi is the founder of Indian
OL,13,FLadies UK, a charity that has
OL,14,Fsupported Harshita's family during
OL,15,Ftheir trip to England. She has also
OL,16,Fcriticised the police's handling of
OL,17,Fher case.
OL,19,F"Harshita was still cooking meals for
OL,20,Fhim every day," she said.
OL,26,@rD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,F"He was free to approach her again. No
OL,8,Fmeaningful safeguarding plan was put
OL,9,Fin place. She was failed by the
OL,10,Fsystem."
OL,12,FFour officers from Northamptonshire
OL,13,FPolice are facing misconduct hearings
OL,14,Fafter the Independent Office for
OL,15,FPolice Conduct found they have a case
OL,16,Fto answer over the way they handled
OL,17,FHarshita's domestic abuse claims.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FThe IOPC concluded two detective
OL,8,Fconstables should have a gross
OL,9,Fmisconduct hearing because they didn't
OL,10,Fappropriately review the case, set
OL,11,Finvestigative actions, seek
OL,12,Fsupervisory advice or keep Harshita
OL,13,Fsufficiently updated. Those hearings
OL,14,Fhave not yet been heard.
OL,16,FTwo more officers, a sergeant and a
OL,17,Fchief inspector who had oversight of
OL,18,Fthe case, had misconduct hearings on
OL,19,FThursday, May 21.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FThose hearings were held in private
OL,8,Fand Harshita's family was not able to
OL,9,Fattend. A summary of that meeting will
OL,10,Fbe published by the force at a later
OL,11,Fdate.
OL,13,FHarshita's family say if her domestic
OL,14,Fabuse allegations had been properly
OL,15,Fhandled, she might still be here today.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FSonia told us: "If they had protected
OL,8,FHarshita, if they had told her she was
OL,9,Fhigh risk, then why (wouldn't she be
OL,10,Fhere)? They didn't keep in touch with
OL,11,Fher. They would just tell her to call
OL,12,Fanother number."
OL,14,FSonia and Harshita's father, Satbir
OL,15,FSingh, met with the senior
OL,16,Finvestigating officer in the case,
OL,17,FDetective Superintendent Johnny
OL,18,FCampbell, Deputy Chief Constable Ash
OL,19,FTuckley, Police Fire and Crime
OL,20,FCommissioner Danielle Stone and other
OL,21,Fmembers of the investigation team.
OL,26,@qD@UpmrD@Epn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1779487871
OL,3,CHarshita Brella's family frustrated
OL,4,Cbut more confident they will get
OL,5,Cjustice
OL,7,FSpeaking after that meeting, Det Supt
OL,8,FCampbell said: "This has been and
OL,9,Fremains an exceptionally complex case
OL,10,Fand we are continuing to work with the
OL,11,Fappropriate agencies in both the UK
OL,12,Fand internationally.
OL,14,F"During the meeting, I was able to
OL,15,Fupdate the family on the live criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings, answer the questions they
OL,17,Fhad, and reassure them of our absolute
OL,18,Fcommitment to secure justice for
OL,19,FHarshita."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
